author: Miss Christine Oates
title: Miss Christine Oates
text: Tractive is a great piece of kit, works well in the woods where we take our dogs, so we can see where our one dog is when he takes him self off!! had to email the firm and received a reply in minutes which sorted my question out, very impressed and would recommend.
